📦 PACKAGE OVERVIEW
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

@componentui/ui
  - Component library with TypeScript + Tailwind CSS
  - Built with Vite for optimal performance
  - Tested with Vitest + React Testing Library
  - Exports: Components, Hooks, Utilities

@componentui/docs
  - Storybook 7 documentation
  - Interactive component examples
  - Accessibility testing with addon-a11y
  - Custom theme configuration

🚀 NEXT STEPS
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

1. Install dependencies:
   $ pnpm install

2. Start Storybook:
   $ pnpm dev:docs

3. Create components in:
   packages/ui/src/components/

4. Add stories in:
   Same directory as component (*.stories.tsx)

5. Run tests:
   $ pnpm test

📚 KEY FEATURES
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

✅ TypeScript 5 with strict mode
✅ Vite for fast builds
✅ Tailwind CSS for styling
✅ Storybook 7 for documentation
✅ Vitest for testing (80% coverage required)
✅ ESLint + Prettier for code quality
✅ Dark mode support
✅ Accessibility focused (WCAG AA)
✅ Tree-shakeable exports
✅ Monorepo with pnpm workspaces
